<span class="description">In paragraph 2, what is one reason that claims such as "the best" or "better than" can be misleading?</span>
<ul>
   <li class="choice">
      <input type="radio"  name="answer-3" value="A">
        They represent the opinions of adults, which are often different from those of children.
      </input>
    </li>
   <li class="choice">
      <input type="radio"  name="answer-3" value="B">
        They generally involve comparisons among only a small group of products.
      </input>
    </li>
   <li class="choice">
      <input type="radio"  name="answer-3" value="C">
